data.description: Enjoy this great, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, 2-story townhome with a 1-car garage in a great gated 55+ community. The soaring vaulted ceiling with wood beam accents and plenty of windows make the home feel open and airy. There is tile on the ground floor, beautiful wood on the iron wrought stairway and engineered wood on the second floor. The kitchen is equipped with newer stainless steel appliances (2020 and 2022), water filtration and breakfast area. The wet bar in the family room and formal dining room are great for entertaining. The primary bedroom offers access to the balcony and a walk-in closet with built-in shelves. One guest bedroom also has a walk-in closet. The primary bathroom is finished with a brand new tub, wall liner and plumbing. The 1/2 bathroom is located on the ground floor for your convenience. The oversized laundry room offers 2022 LG washer and dryer. Relax on your covered screened-in (2019) patio in the quiet, beautifully landscaped, private and fenced backyard. Other notable features include 2023 painted interior, new balcony, sealed roof over the garage, newer light fixtures, impact front window and door, accordion shutters with a roll down in the primary bedroom. The AC was replaced in 2023, water heater in 2020 and the roof in 2010. The TV mount, refrigerator on the patio and shelves in the third bedroom will stay. Furniture is negotiable. Rosedale at Indian Springs is a great development featuring a nice community pool. It is conveniently located to grocery stores and shopping plazas. Take a quick ride to the lively downtown Delray Beach Atlantic Ave. or Renaissance Commons featuring many amazing restaurants and shops. The development is in close proximity to I-95, Turnpike, and the beach. All measurements are approximate. Take a look at 3D virtual walkthrough.
